---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="GLANCE Apps is an independent software studio making calm, focused tools for iOS, Android, and macOS."
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-accent mb-6">
        About
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-glance-text leading-tight mb-12">
        Small studio.<br />Careful work.
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          GLANCE Apps is an independent software studio building quiet, careful
          tools that earn a place in your daily life without demanding more
          attention than they give back. The studio started with a simple
          frustration: productivity apps had become noisy, complicated, and
          self-important. We wanted something quieter. So we built it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every app in the GLANCE family shares the same values: restraint in
          design, depth in function, and respect for the person using it. We
          don't add features for the sake of them. We ship when something is
          genuinely ready.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're one developer, working independently, building apps we actually
          use every day.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 pt-10 section-rule">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
          Open Source
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          <p>
            GLANCE Apps is an open source software publisher. The source code for
            every app is freely available on GitHub:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent shrink-0">·</span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">dayGLANCE</strong>:
                <a href="https://github.com/krelltunez/dayGLANCE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-glance-accent link-underline">github.com/krelltunez/dayGLANCE</a>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent shrink-0">·</span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">lifeGLANCE</strong>:
                <a href="https://github.com/krelltunez/lifeGLANCE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-glance-accent link-underline">github.com/krelltunez/lifeGLANCE</a>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-glance-accent shrink-0">·</span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">lastGLANCE</strong>:
                <a href="https://github.com/krelltunez/lastGLANCE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-glance-accent link-underline">github.com/krelltunez/lastGLANCE</a>
                <span class="text-glance-dim">(coming soon)</span>
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Apps distributed through the Apple App Store and Google Play Store are
            commercial binaries that support continued development. The source code
            remains MIT licensed and freely available for self-hosting, modification,
            or audit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 pt-10 section-rule grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Values
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-glance-accent">·</span> Calm over noise</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-glance-accent">·</span> Depth over breadth</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-glance-accent">·</span> Privacy as default</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-glance-accent">·</span> Ship slowly, ship well</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted mb-3">
            Questions, feedback, or just want to say hello?
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-accent link-underline"
          >
            Get in touch →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
